Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:27.46,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1462294,1467466}Tsukikage and Ondine are both participating\Nin the Tōkyō prefectural drama contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.46,0:24:30.21,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1467466,1470219}and both have chosen to perform "Growing Up".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.21,0:24:34.72,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1470219,1474723}Midori, the main role, will be played by\NKitajima Maya and Himekawa Ayumi.{NOTE:主役のみどりをやるのは北島マヤと姫川亜弓}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.72,0:24:38.22,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1474723,1478227}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"The Lonely Battle".{NOTE:ガラスの仮面 孤独な戦いを楽しみに}
